# PocketBase URL
# Development: http://127.0.0.1:8090
# Production: https://your-pocketbase-instance.com
VITE_POCKETBASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8090

# OAuth2 Credentials
# These are configured in PocketBase Admin UI (_/ → Settings → Auth providers)
# NOT as environment variables
#
# You'll need to create OAuth2 apps at:
# - Spotify: https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard
# - Google: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#
# Then add Client ID and Secret in PocketBase Admin UI